name: power
description: The topology of the Western States Power Grid of the United States.

graph.semantic: The topology of the Western States Power Grid of the United States.

qares.question: which node has the highest degree in the graph?
qares.query:
SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.grap@y7x4uj graph.property.node_members ?e1.
e1? node.property.degree ?e2} ORDER BY DESC(?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the lowest centrality in the graph?
qares.query:
SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.grap@y7x4uj graph.property.node_members ?e1.
e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY (?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the highest centrality that links with node “1”?
qares.query:
SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.node@1 node.property.link_with ?e1.
e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY DESC(?e2) LIMIT 1

qares.question: what is the node with the lowest centrality in community 1?
qares.query:
SELECT ?e1 WHERE { m.comm@p_2pkd community.property.contain_nodes ?e1.
e1? node.property.degree_centrality ?e2} ORDER BY (?e2) LIMIT 1
